{"id": "1358366865055023226", "channel_id": "1356870413791006811", "type": 0, "author_id": "1213364721328332840", "author_name": "akalanden", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是硬要說的話，我的猜測是星辰的劇本偏向於一個整體，而忘卻的劇本更像是單元劇每集一個小故事", "timestamp": "2025-04-06T09:04:57.865000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-06T09:06:16.513000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356870413791006811", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜克萊門汀┊喚醒體&命輪介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1358368226261729442", "channel_id": "1356870413791006811", "type": 0, "author_id": "1213364721328332840", "author_name": "akalanden", "author_bot": false, "content": "忘卻一是倫蒂尼恩失蹤案，二是幫助鼠鼠找姐姐，三四則是調查地獄犬等等，中心劇情很明確\n星辰一是什麼，我們在幹什麼，打B-68是為了什麼，各章節劇情中心過於薄弱了導致沒有記憶點", "timestamp": "2025-04-06T09:10:22.402000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-06T09:38:25.291000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356870413791006811", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜克萊門汀┊喚醒體&命輪介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1358368840563556453", "channel_id": "1356870413791006811", "type": 0, "author_id": "1213364721328332840", "author_name": "akalanden", "author_bot": false, "content": "想來想去，最終還是理解為~~招安~~，其實應該是星辰整體中心劇情關於強烈，導致章節劇情體現不足", "timestamp": "2025-04-06T09:12:48.863000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-06T09:20:40.724000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356870413791006811", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜克萊門汀┊喚醒體&命輪介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1358369050555715797", "channel_id": "1356870413791006811", "type": 0, "author_id": "1213364721328332840", "author_name": "akalanden", "author_bot": false, "content": "招安融朵，招安克萊門汀，最後舉行星辰正位的儀式（？）", "timestamp": "2025-04-06T09:13:38.929000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356870413791006811", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜克萊門汀┊喚醒體&命輪介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1358376352063160331", "channel_id": "1356870413791006811", "type": 19, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "忘卻其實就很標準的章節單元劇埋暗線~~原來我玩的TRPG嗎~~雕塑家過渡到提燈這樣\n至於星辰就和你說的一樣，是一個整體，因為劇情情報吐露的不多搞得看起來不知所云，忘卻前夜的劇情個人看來已經是中等水平，應該不會暴太大雷了（自動遺忘朵爾失憶", "timestamp": "2025-04-06T09:42:39.744000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1213364721328332840"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1358366865055023226", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356870413791006811", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜克萊門汀┊喚醒體&命輪介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1358417894475694131", "channel_id": "1356870413791006811", "type": 0, "author_id": "484555315447332864", "author_name": "randomplayer852", "author_bot": false, "content": "关于银钥充能我问个问题。目前塔维命轮给的百分比银钥充能提高并没有体现在角色面板上（编队点开唤醒体的详细信息面板）。\n别的很多游戏为了防止左脚踩右脚，很多转模设计都只计算的面板数值。克莱门汀天赋里 银钥充能转暴击爆伤，是否会计入命轮给的百分比银钥充能提高带来的额外银钥充能。\n<@633215996508766229>", "timestamp": "2025-04-06T12:27:44.227000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356870413791006811", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜克萊門汀┊喚醒體&命輪介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1358418733034639430", "channel_id": "1356870413791006811", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "不会，百分比效果指实际充能效果。属性则特指各来源提供的属性。", "timestamp": "2025-04-06T12:31:04.155000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["484555315447332864"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1358417894475694131", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356870413791006811", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "📜克萊門汀┊喚醒體&命輪介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
